* I hope this code supports all future extensions on the graphics
  chipset, because all handling is done via the graphics.library's
  'DisplayInfoDataBase'. According to Commodore Frankfurt, the AAA chipset
  is going to be out in Autumn 1994, so we'll see...

* And this is the To-Do-List:
